<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Event Reminder</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
  <div style="max-width:600px;margin:20px auto;padding:20px;border:1px solid #ddd;">
    <h3>Hello {{userName}},</h3>
    <p>This is a friendly reminder that <strong>{{eventName}}</strong> is starting soon!</p>
    <p>Date & Time: {{startDate}} - {{endDate}}<br/>
       Location: {{location}}</p>
    <p>We hope to see you there!</p>
    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us.</p>
    <p>Regards,<br/>Event Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
